Sales Manager - OIL & GAS
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/04/30 06:13:52
Ref. JB3038875
Job Description
This job vacancy is for our sister concern MASKEM- Dubai
ESSENTIAL FUNCTIONS :
• Lead strategic relationships/partnerships with key customers in the O&G; industry resulting in sales of Co. products across all industry segments. Coordinate execution and drive to closure
• Identify growth opportunities for well stimulation and enhanced oil recovery products
in customers’ operations
• Identify and champion new products, commercial strategies, and partnership opportunities to grow the Co. portfolio
• Partner with the Co. technical team in Germany to identify and promote existing products, new solutions, potential technical partnerships and demonstrations
• Responsible for Co. brand and reputation management throughout the region.
• Represent the Co. in appropriate forums and be a spokesperson for the company
Skills
QUALIFICATION
• Technical degree
• MBA in marketing, business or related disciplines
• Minimum of 10 years of experience encompassing sales, marketing, business development, or project management in the O&G; industry or relevant supply chain
• Strong networking and relationships with major oil & gas companies, downstream companies, ministries,
and public sector enterprises in GCC region
• Experience in selling to and influencing large, complex organizations
IDEAL PREVIOUS EXPERIENCE :
• Prior experience of selling products and solutions to key accounts in the O&G; industry
• Prior experience in oilfield chemicals for well stimulation, hydraulic fracturing and enhanced oil recovery projects
• Clear understanding of technical and commercial challenges in the O&G; industry
• Strong track record for generating measurable results, including exceeding op plans, driving growth and generating new customers
• Strong commercial instincts, ability to partner effectively with sales, marketing, product management teams and communications, with a reputation for execution
• Strong executive presence and experience in dealing with C-level suite execs
SKILLS & COMPETENCIES :
• Able to analyze, interpret, draw conclusions, and implement solutions on a variety of complex issues.
Individual must be self-focusing and be able to drive the critical few priorities in an environment where many demands and requests present themselves.
• Able to work independently. Formulate and execute a self-driven plan
• Able to organize, prioritize, and manage multiple projects simultaneously with appropriate sense of urgency
• Able to quickly learn about new industries, customers and technologies and translate value to customers
• Should be a clear thinker with a structured mind;
• Have excellent verbal and written communication skills, including presentation skills.
• Able to function as a member of a team – strong interpersonal skills
• Be a critical and creative thinker with imagination and self-confidence
This job is posted in the following Specialties:
Education
MBA in Marketing, business or related disciplines
